transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Ji bhaiya.
Executive: Sir, woh aapka live toh ho gaya woh wala service, theek hai. But usme KYC abhi pending hai. Aapke hamari team koi call kar rahe hai but aapke wahan se koi response nahi aa raha. Hai na? Toh woh abhi bhi still pending hi hai. But woh live ho gaya hai. MDC service live hai.
Customer: Haan woh leads nahi mil pa rahi na sir, usme leads nahi mil pa rahi.
Executive: Leads toh mil hi raha hoga.
Customer: Nahi.
Executive: Leads nahi mil pa rahi.
Executive: Uska pehle KYC aap complete karwaiye sir. Sabse pehle woh toh pending hai. Woh aap complete karwayenge fir jaake kuch ho payega. Aapke account manager bhi assigned ho jayenge. Kya naam hai aapka Abhishek? Abhishek assigned bhi ho gaye hai aapko account manager.
Customer: Chaliye main check karwata hu, theek hai.
Executive: Haan usko check karaiye aur yeh wala jo number hai, ek baar dikhana sir woh purane jo number hai.
Customer: Yeh wala starting mein jo.
Executive: Haan ek aapne jo number de rakha hai na IndiaMART pe yeh 207 hai last mein.
Customer: Yeh toh mera hai.
Executive: Achha. 207 toh koi nahi. 75 750 hai.
Customer: 75 yeh bhi nahi hai bhaiya koi number.
Executive: 93158067.
Customer: 9315. No no yeh number nahi hai bhaiya hamara.
Executive: Yeh nahi hai? Yeh galti se shayad woh add kar diya.
Executive: Yahan pe click karna chart pe. Chart pe click karo ek bari.
Executive: Ispe calls pe jaana hai.
Executive: Ah, 02
Executive: 020 hai na koi yeh number 74 se start hai.
Customer: 02 74 se start hai.
Executive: Nahi 74 se toh yeh wala number hoga 741.
Customer: 020 last mein hai. Yeh number aapka de rakha hai. Team hamari call kar rahi hai.
Customer: Nahi nahi yeh number nahi hai mera bhaiya yeh toh kisi aur ka number hai.
Executive: Catalog banwate time mein aapne number diya tha hoga na. Jo Easy ko.
Customer: Sir jo number hai na yeh 020 toh yeh pura number hi hoga 7417428020.
Executive: 8020 aa raha hai.
Customer: 020 aa raha hai isme ji.
Executive: Yahi wala hoga.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Is wale se aap IndiaMART login kar pa rahe hai?
Customer: Ji kar pa raha hu. Isi se hi login hai.
Executive: Isi se login hai. Toh isi pe toh call ja rahi hai fir hamare team pe. Team ka yeh hame toh mail bhi aa rakha hai.
Customer: Call nahi kiya woh last time toh.
Executive: Dikhana last call kab gayi thi team hamari kab ki thi?
Customer: Last call aaj hi gaya tha sir 10:37 pe bhi gayi thi.
Customer: Aaj gayi hai?
Executive: Haan aaj bhi gayi 10:37 pe.
Executive: Ashish Singh koi karke hai woh aapko call kar rahe hai.
Customer: Okay okay chaliye.
Executive: Usse return ho jayegi call back?
Executive: Ah nahi nahi return toh nahi hogi. Main call back arrange karwa sakta hu uske liye.
Customer: Sir abhi woh number dusre unke paas hai jo mere partner hai. Toh unko bol deta hu. Theek hai. Aap thoda late call karwaiye 1 baje ke baad keh dijiye unko.
Executive: 1 baje ke baad. Theek hai.
Customer: Ji ji. Isme update daal dena ki 1 baje sir ko call chahiye. Theek hai. Abhi yeh haan yeh Abhishek Ashish Singh hai woh. Inko yeh update daal do aap.
Executive: Ki inko sir ko 1 baje ke around call chahiye.
Customer: Main daal deta hu.
Executive: Mail bhi toh aaya hoga inka.
Executive: Yeh not contactable ka mail bhi hai kar sakte hai in log. Ashish Singh koi mil rahe honge check karo.
Executive: Main ek baar call back arrange karwa deta hu sir iske liye. Theek hai.
Customer: Theek theek hai sir.
Executive: Aur yeh wala jo aapka abhi call line hua tha na yeh hamare pe hua tha. Theek hai yeh jo gas wala jo aapka.
Customer: Ji ji.
Executive: Woh mere mere wale catalog pe koi dikkat samasya hai toh bataiye fir.
Customer: Nahi nahi koi dikkat nahi hai sir.
Executive: Toh is wale se aapke complaint open hua toh main isko close kar raha hu fir. Theek hai?
Customer: Theek theek hai.
Executive: Aur iska na ek mail aapko receive hoga sir.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Mail receive hoga jisme aapko yeh usme mention hoga ki haan aap satisfied hai ki nahi. Toh yeh wale se aap satisfied mark kar dijiyega please. Aur aapko na future mein agar kabhi dobara uske liye aapko related kuch jaankari chahiye hoga na toh main Abhishek ji ka ek toh number aapko drop kar de raha hu jo us wale company ka hai. Theek hai?
Executive: Aapke WhatsApp pe. Theek hai us wale account account manager ke paas woh hai na toh unka main WhatsApp pe number drop kar de raha hu. Aur agar call bhi karna hoga 9696 pe na toh aap kar sakte hai lekin sir ke number se kariyega jo 8020 wala number hai.
Customer: Theek theek hai theek hai.
Executive: Haan kyunki is wale se karenge toh fir mere paas hi aapka complaint open ho payega.
Customer: Okay okay okay okay theek hai theek hai.
Executive: Haan kyunki jo primary registered hota hai usi se hum complaint open kar sakte hai. Aap yeh cheez dhyan rakhiyega.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai. Baki main close kar raha hu sir okay. Main number bhi drop kar raha hu aapke WhatsApp pe.
Customer: Theek hai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer is not receiving leads.

- Customer states the number is not his.



Resolution:

- Executive asked to complete KYC first.

- Executive will arrange a call back at 1 PM.

- Executive is closing the complaint.

- Executive shared account manager number on WhatsApp.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will add a note for callback at 1 PM.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied
